snippet.title: Milkblood Trailer
snippet.description:
Milkblood is a tiny game about dying a lot an making a huge mess.
It was created in one week by Shanahan Sweet for the 9th Brackeys game jam, and features music by RoccoW.

You can play the game for free right here: https://valknut.itch.io/milkblood

The music in this trailer was created by The Playliszt - 8-bit Music, and can be enjoyed here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MQ61ZoWohgQ
